templates.risk_assessment_content:
Please assess the risk of the following Energy AI System:

System Info:
- Name: {system_name}
- Purpose: {purpose}
- Data Types: {data_types}
- User Impact: {impact_level}

Evaluation Criteria:
1. Privacy Risk (1-10)
2. Energy Grid Stability Impact (1-10)
3. Regulatory Compliance Necessity (1-10)
4. Social Impact (1-10)

Please provide scores and rationale for each item, and determine the overall risk level (LOW/MEDIUM/HIGH/CRITICAL).

templates.bias_analysis_content:
Please analyze the bias of the following Energy Dataset:

Dataset Info:
- Data Type: {data_type}
- Collection Period: {collection_period}
- Data Size: {data_size}
- Regional Distribution: {regional_distribution}

Analysis Items:
1. Regional Bias (Capital vs Local)
2. Temporal Bias (Peak vs Off-peak)
3. Seasonal Bias (Summer vs Winter)
4. User Group Bias (Age, Income, Household Type)

Please provide the degree of bias (0-1 scale) and mitigation strategies for each.
